programme.desc: Elis' mother is worried about Ira, her daughter who is dating Andra. Ira doesn't realize that Andra is a playboy. Elis' mother did not agree with Ira continuing her relationship with Andra because Andra had hit Elis' mother twice while on the highway.

programme.title: Prince Of Rock And Roll
programme.desc: Zein loves rock n roll. Meanwhile, his father is filthy rich and wanted to make him his sucessor, but the unwilling Zein ran away. He then met Maura, a pretty and hard working woman.

programme.title: Teror Malam Jum'at
programme.desc: Dina, a clumsy but smart student, is used by Gerry, Viola, and Bianca, naughty and lazy students, to do their college assignments. Annoyed by the sinister of Dina's friends, Bima, Dina's elder brother, takes revenge and terrorizes them.

programme.title: Tulah Pedagang Nasi Goreng Yang Dengki
programme.desc: Mrs. Ati, the fried rice seller, jealous when she saw Bang Umar was opening a fried rice stall in front of hers. Then, she did everything she could to make Bang Umar's stall close down, but what she did actually became a disaster for her.

programme.title: Catatan Terakhir Rara
programme.desc: Rara doesn't get enough attention from her parents, so Rara is often teased by her friends at school. Soon, Rara gets cancer which made her parents realize to live together and happy as before.

programme.title: Ondel-Ondel Cinta Arinda
programme.desc: Arinda is getting an ultimatum by her parents to immediately finish her thesis, or else, they will take back all of her accomodations. But Imam, her source for her thesis about ondel-ondel instead made Arinda's life more complicated.

programme.title: Susu Kedelai Penarik Arwah
programme.desc: After surviving a plane accident, Ken went home to give a surprise to his family and girlfriend. But alas, he instead came home to his own funeral.

programme.title: Kalau Lupa Jangan Cinta
programme.desc: Neneng, an innocent village girl comes to Jakarta to find Ujang, her boyfriend. Neneng is invited to stay at Alfian's house without her parents understanding. A commotion ensues at home when Nadya, Alfian's girlfriend comes to Alfian's house.

programme.title: P.P.T - Pacarku Pacar Temenku
programme.desc: Firly gets awkward with Alex, a mischievous guy in his office, there are always disputes between them. But the love between them grows and they're dating. On the other hand, Alex already has a girlfriend, Karin, Firly's friend.

programme.title: Ngarep Wedding Dot Com
programme.desc: Karina works at a dating agency that helps people find their other half. Sasha, a single girl, asks Karina to find a man of her dreams. However, Sasha unexpectedly likes Cikho, Karina's boyfriend.

programme.title: Suara Pemanggil Sukma
programme.desc: Due to financial struggle, a girl resorts to stealing to afford food. But her life changed one day when she found out that her stolen goods are supernatural hallows.

programme.title: Super Cepot Beraksi 2
programme.desc: Wanti, Burhan, and Jerry plot to separate Cecep the puppet from Lala. They do good things to Lala in order to carry out their scheming. When Lala and Cecep are deceived, Wanti and her friends sell Cecep to the circus owner.

programme.title: Undian Berhadiah Cinta
programme.desc: Naya is fed up with her parents who are obsessed to marry her off to their rich neighbour. Angrily, she eats her favorite chocolate, but unexpectedly, she won a lottery from it!

programme.title: Sweet Martabak Buat Kamu Yang Manis
programme.desc: The sweet taste are delicious like martabak, especially the martabak seller is also a cute man. Kenang, the cute martabak seller who enchanting girls, is really good at making martabak. But why Kenang and Jingga often fighting?

programme.title: Moshi-Moshi
programme.desc: To Meliana, Julio Alexander is everything she ever dreamed about. He's her truly male idol. Even Mel always imagined what it feels to date him. Eventually, her dream came true even though she already has a boyfriend, Thomas.

programme.title: Soulmate Yang Tertukar
programme.desc: Fajar is a photographer who has a model girlfriend. Despite their differences, Fajar is sure that he's in it for the long run. But, an encounter made him question that belief.

programme.title: Bidadari From Angkot
programme.desc: Aisyah, a beautiful public transportation driver, is a center attention for all including Rafael. A rich guy who is in love with Aisyah even though Rafael has a girlfriend. Aisyah often gets ridicule from her friends on campus, because she is a public transportation driver.

programme.title: Mantan Yang Tak Diundang
programme.desc: Whilst walking with her boyfriend, Kiena met David, her former boyfriend. Yosha, Kiena's boyfriend, is annoyed with David, who often takes Kiena go out. Did Kiena stay loyal to Yosha? Or will she be back with her ex?

programme.title: Toko Kr.Amat : Amplop Bertuah
programme.desc: Maya and Eva are sisters, but Maya's face is not as beautiful as her sister, Eva. One day, Maya meets a beggar and gives her an envelope that will grant all her wishes. Maya becomes complacent and arrogant until disaster befell her.

programme.title: Selendang Pemikat
programme.desc: In order to look beautiful and attract men, Lilis wears a charm shawl. However, Lilis has to offer a sacrifice so that the shawl will grant all her wishes. In Fact, the shawl brought disaster to her and her father

programme.title: Biola Tak Bertuan
programme.desc: Vanesha moves into a new house inhabited by the ghost of a man named Edy Samudera. He was a violinist who committed suicide 35 years ago and left a legendary violin worth millions of dollars.

programme.title: Catatan Terakhir Rara
programme.desc: Rara doesn't get enough attention from her parents, so Rara is often teased by her friends at school. Soon, Rara gets cancer which made her parents realize to live together and happy as before.

programme.title: Made In Betawi
programme.desc: Heartbroken after being left behing by his first love, Made, a Balinese, asked to go to Jakarta to give something precious and important to someone there. Hoping for the best, he accepted that task.

programme.title: Cincin Hilang Cintapun Datang
programme.desc: Nabila accidentally bumps into Afgan who is holding a ring, making it falls and lost. Nabila and Afgan try to find the ring. From this encounter, the seeds of love grew between them.

programme.title: Qurban Belahan Hati
programme.desc: Raka, a devout and kind guy, saved money to buy a cow for Eid Adha. Tiara, Raka's girlfriend, is annoyed because Raka prefers to take her to the cowshed instead of the mall or buying her a ring.

programme.title: Kucing Garong Vs Kucing Dapur
programme.desc: Rere has to be patient with Bisma, her playboy boyfriend. But it turns out that Bisma made a pass at Bella, Rere's best friend. What will happen?

programme.title: Nakula Dan Sadewa
